like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"毋忘831 pepe 心心拖<br />\n<br />\n轉發<br />\n「大家可能會好奇點解會有9月30日呢個pepe 心心拖既活動意義<br />\n係因為831一個月，好多迷團都未解開，想大家拎個良心出黎，要求黨鐵／政府公開交代事件，眾說紛紜，希望可以悉除公眾疑慮。<br />\n至於叫pepe 心心拖係因為我地希望將pepe化作愛既表現等大家用愛連結呢個香港💚<br />\n心理心，we connected。<br />\n特有既pepe心心摺紙都公開比大家下載了。<br />\n燈籠則代表燃點希望，為香港人打打氣，成個活動主題以綠色為主。<br />\n特有既pepe摺紙燈籠都公開比大家下載了。<br />\n<br />\n所選地點鐘樓則代表光明處，希望香港人可以走到光明處。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家發揮大家既創意，整貼紙／幫pepe化妝、做人體彩繪、紋身、諸如此類去一齊渡過一個和平既pepe晚上！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1poxz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1poxz1.jpg&h=64592520&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxcxqU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoxcxqU2.jpg&h=928b933f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LK9oxz3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLK9oxz3.jpg&h=a54b4ade&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjLV78p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjLV78p.jpg&h=290cda1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRCEQmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRCEQmN.jpg&h=c12e86ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kus13GS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkus13GS.jpg&h=692eab83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbhUEfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbhUEfd.jpg&h=96b01e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRHUEff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRHUEff.jpg&h=29cc7da0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1QCB1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1QCB1X.jpg&h=65e8c91d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dfrm3GY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%